headline: Public Storage Declares Third Quarter 2025 Dividends
summary: GLENDALE, Calif., August 26, 2025--Public Storage (NYSE:PSA) announced today that on August 26, 2025, our Board of Trustees declared a regular quarterly common dividend of $3.00 per common share. The Board also declared dividends with respect to our various series of preferred shares. All the dividends are payable on September 30, 2025, to shareholders of record as of September 15, 2025.

headline: Wells Fargo upgrades Extra Space amid improving outlook for self-storage
summary: Investing.com -- Wells Fargo raised its rating on Extra Space Storage to Overweight from Equal Weight, saying the self-storage operator looks best positioned among peers as the sector shows signs of stabilizing after a weak start to the year.
